getData

ChannelBuffer getData()
Returns the data payload of this frame. If there is no data payload ChannelBuffers.EMPTY_BUFFER is returned.

setData

void setData(ChannelBuffer data)
Sets the data payload of this frame. If null is specified, the data payload will be set to ChannelBuffers.EMPTY_BUFFER. The data payload cannot exceed 16777215 bytes.
